# ===========================================
# COMMENTS FOR REFERENCE
# ===========================================
# This .gitignore is designed for:
# 1. Python ML/DL projects with PyTorch
# 2. Image processing projects
# 3. Streamlit applications
# 4. Projects with large datasets and model files
#
# Remember to:
# - Use Git LFS for large files if needed
# - Document dataset download instructions in README
# - Keep model architecture code but not weights
# - Maintain requirements.txt for reproducibility